law.history: Repealed 1974 Ky. Acts ch. 130, sec. 198, effective June 21, 1974. -- Amended 1964 Ky. Acts ch. 142, sec. 7. -- Amended 1948 Ky. Acts ch. 81, sec. 5. -- Recodified 1942 Ky. Acts ch. 208, sec. 1, effective October 1, 1942, from Ky. Stat. secs. 1550-1c, 1550-1e, 1550-1f, 1550-5.

metadata.catchline-at-repeal: Political parties must nominate candidates by primary -- Exceptions -- Vacancy in nomination.
